          <div class="comment-content"> 
           <p>No Northwestern, Fordham, Yale, or Brown? Northwestern especially ranked in the top 10 of all programs in the country, undergraduate, graduate, BA, BFA, MFA, etc. Without a doubt it should be #1, with Fordham, Yale, and Brown following close behind in terms of BAs.</p> 
           <p id="comment-like-564" data-liked="comment-not-liked" class="comment-likes comment-not-liked"><a href="http://onstageblog.com/2015/02/19/the-best-b-a-in-theatre-programs-in-the-country-in-2015/?like_comment=564&amp;_wpnonce=1e88e18e5e" class="comment-like-link needs-login" rel="nofollow" data-blog="71050352"><span>Like</span></a><span id="comment-like-count-564" class="comment-like-feedback">Like</span></p> 
