          <!-- .comment-meta --> 
          <div class="comment-content"> 
           <p>Georgia College is honored to be among your Honorable Mentions for Best B.A. programs in Theatre. Our undergraduates get lead roles even as freshmen and our students design mainstage shows. These same students direct mainstage shows as seniors. We are proud of our students and program which has developed a world premiere and performed it off-Broadway. Thank you for this honor!</p> 
           <p id="comment-like-605" data-liked="comment-not-liked" class="comment-likes comment-not-liked"><a href="http://onstageblog.com/2015/02/19/the-best-b-a-in-theatre-programs-in-the-country-in-2015/?like_comment=605&amp;_wpnonce=b7f6f9e636" class="comment-like-link needs-login" rel="nofollow" data-blog="71050352"><span>Like</span></a><span id="comment-like-count-605" class="comment-like-feedback">Liked by <a href="#" class="view-likers" data-like-count="1">1 person</a></span></p> 
